
************************************
  SMC - Semantic Mapping Component
************************************

SMC is a module within the CMDI framework [1] of the CLARIN infrastructure.

It provides mappings between fields in heterogeneous metadata descriptions
building on top of Data Category Registry (ISOcat [2])

[1] http://clarin.eu/cmdi
[2] http://isocat.org

Overview
--------

The code consists mainly of XSL-stylesheets 
[src/scripts/*.xsl]
and a minimal Java "application" (meant mainly to invoke the initialization steps)
[src/eu/clarin/cmdi/smc/SMC.java]


